[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0186","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0186.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0211","title":"Red Hat Linux 6.0/6.1 Linuxconf 程序 CGI 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 6.0 与 6.1 中自带的 linuxconf 程序存在安全缺陷，其提供的 CGI 接口在处理请求时未对用户输入进行充分校验，攻击者可构造特定的 HTTP 请求访问 /lcfg 等路径，从而读取系统中的配置文件与敏感信息，导致信息泄露，攻击仅需向目标 Web 服务发送特制请求即可完成。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0211"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-22","updated":"2000-02-22","remediation":"升级 linuxconf 至官方修复版本（Red Hat 6.1 更新后可修复），或移除 Web 服务器中 linuxconf 的 CGI 脚本并禁用相关访问路径，限制 /lcfg 等敏感路径的外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2000-02-22T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0211","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1000"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0186.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0500","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0500.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0160","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer ActiveX Active Setup 未授权软件安装漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.x 和 5.x 中的 Microsoft Active Setup ActiveX 组件存在安全验证缺陷，未能正确校验软件发布者的真实身份。远程攻击者可构造恶意网页，通过伪造软件制造商为 \"Microsoft\" 的方式，诱使受害者访问后在不弹出安全确认提示的情况下静默安装任意软件组件。利用该漏洞无需用户明确授权，攻击条件仅需目标用户使用受影响版本的 IE 浏览器并打开攻击者控制的页面，可能导致恶意代码在用户系统上被安装和执行，进而危害系统安全。CVSS 评分 7.6，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0160"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:07.510","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 1 或更高版本以修复该 Active Setup ActiveX 组件缺陷。如无法立即升级，可在 Internet Explorer 的「安全设置」中将 ActiveX 控件和插件设为「禁用」或「提示」，并在组策略中禁用未签名 ActiveX 安装，同时限制可信站点区域以阻止远程静默安装软件组件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-15&msg=20000221103938.T21312%40securityfocus.com","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b3f84cd2bd659a86c86b8cfbfca1a01084368c06/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0160.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0160","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0160.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0160.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xwwx-jfc6-33fv/GHSA-xwwx-jfc6-33fv.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0160.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/27329332eaf6d7802a105e6a6dc78246a75b7339/2000.tsv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/999/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0500.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0509","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0509.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0166","title":"Pragma Systems InterAccess TelnetD Server 4.0 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Pragma Systems InterAccess TelnetD Server 4.0 Build 4的recv()函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向Telnet服务发送超长登录名触发溢出，导致服务CPU占用率达到100%或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响Build 4（1998年5月4日构建）及更早版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0166"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-21","updated":"2000-02-23","remediation":"升级到InterAccess TelnetD Server 4.0 Build 7（2000年1月5日发布）或更高版本，并安装最新的Windows NT服务包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T04:12:53.488624547+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95142756403323&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/995","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=NCBBKFKDOLAGKIAPMILPGEJHCCAA.labs%40ussrback.com"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0509.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0185","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0185.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0210","title":"Sun FlexLM lit 符号链接本地文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Sun Flex License Manager（FlexLM）中的 lit 程序在处理文件时未对符号链接进行安全检查，会直接跟随符号链接进行操作。本地已登录用户可以创建指向任意系统文件的符号链接，诱使 lit 程序以该程序权限写入或覆盖目标文件，从而修改本无权访问的任意文件内容。该漏洞影响运行 Sun Workshop 5.0 等使用 FlexLM 授权管理组件的 Solaris 系统，攻击前提是攻击者需在目标主机拥有本地账户及执行 lit 程序的权限，属于本地权限提升类漏洞，CVSS 评分较低（约 1.2），危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0210"],"sources":["exploitdb","cve"],"published":"2000-02-21","updated":"2026-07-19","remediation":"立即停用或卸载 Sun Workshop 5.0 中的 FlexLM 组件；将 lit 可执行文件去除 setuid 位（chmod u-s /path/to/lit）并限制普通用户对其执行权限；确保 /tmp 等临时目录设置 sticky bit（chmod 1777 /tmp）且仅 root 可写敏感目标文件。若业务仍需许可证服务，迁移到已修复的后续 FlexNet Publisher 或 Oracle Solaris Studio 授权方案，并禁止本地非特权用户在 lit 工作目录创建符号链接；无法升级时，将 lit 从默认 PATH 移除并配合严格本地账户与文件 ACL 作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/998","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19757","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad13a04165adf44a190b93c89d746f49525e5595/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0210.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0185.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0185.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0185.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0145","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0145.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0163","title":"FreeBSD asmon/ascpu 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 3.0至3.4版本中ports套件的Asmon和Ascpu工具存在本地权限提升漏洞。这两个工具是AfterStep窗口管理器的applet，因需要访问/dev/kmem而被设置为setgid kmem。本地攻击者可通过-e命令行选项传入恶意参数，诱使这些工具以kmem组权限执行任意命令，从而获得系统敏感信息访问权限。该漏洞影响FreeBSD 3.x系列多个版本，CVSS评分4.6，危害等级中危。由于需要本地访问权限，攻击条件相对受限，但一旦利用成功可提升至kmem组权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0163"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-21","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 FreeBSD 3.5 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可移除 asmon 和 ascpu 的 setgid 权限：chmod u-s /usr/local/bin/asmon /usr/local/bin/ascpu，并限制配置文件仅允许 root 用户写入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/996","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/advisory.html?id=2092","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19756"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0145.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0145.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0145.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0146","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0146.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0164","title":"Sun Internet Mail Server 密码泄露漏洞","description":"Sun Internet Mail Server 密码泄露漏洞","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0164"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:08.017","remediation":"Sun Internet Mail Server (SIMS) 已停止维护，建议迁移至 Oracle Communications Messaging Server 或其它受支持的邮件服务器。临时缓解措施：以 root 身份执行 `chmod 640 /etc/mail/sims.conf /etc/mail/sims.passwd` 限制配置文件权限，并移除全局可读权限；同时检查 `/var/mail` 下是否存在权限过松的密码缓存文件，确保仅 mail 管理员组可读。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1004","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-15&msg=Pine.SOL.4.21.0002200031320.22675-100000%40klayman.hq.formus.pl","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5546763f2cbf8b9d0a5bd1b009f21d50c3edeb8b/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0164.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0164","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0164.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1eab609178bfac1fdc1fdc37b8b4d17d9ecf98b7/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0164.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j5f3-8x75-9w2c/GHSA-j5f3-8x75-9w2c.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0164.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001179.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ec3be0baed1eb129c466b944014a0769e187fd54/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0146.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0144","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0144.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0162","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer Virtual Machine 远程任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.x 和 5.x 内置的 Microsoft Java 虚拟机（VM）存在沙箱逃逸漏洞。远程攻击者可通过构造恶意的 Java Applet 程序，使其绕过 Java 安全沙箱的限制，从而在当前用户权限下读取目标系统上的任意本地文件。该漏洞影响使用 IE 4.x/5.x 且启用 Java 虚拟机的 Windows 系统，攻击条件为诱导受害者访问攻击者控制的网页并加载恶意 Applet，无需身份认证即可在客户端触发，可能导致敏感信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0162"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:07.757","remediation":"建议立即通过 Windows Update 安装微软 2000 年 4 月发布的安全更新（MS00-024，对应 VM 版本 5.0.0.3805 及以上），升级 Internet Explorer 内置的 Microsoft VM 以修补沙箱逃逸缺陷。若暂无法打补丁，应在 IE 中禁用 Java（工具→Internet 选项→安全→自定义级别→禁用 Java 小程序）或暂时禁用 Java 以阻断恶意 applet 读取本地文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-011","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c707cc2908b5d07c1aaeed7fd0c79e5c6b4bb826/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0162.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0162","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0162.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/aeda8c7b429aa1dfdb16de3b1ae154a7b870f9be/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0162.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pc2c-8pxg-2287/GHSA-pc2c-8pxg-2287.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0162.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d98ad802-81b5-480a-839d-a4f8b4b58d75.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001178.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/957/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0144.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0139","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0139.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0155","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 autorun.inf 本地代码执行漏洞","description":"Windows NT 的自动运行功能在处理非可移动介质上的 autorun.inf 文件时存在代码注入漏洞。本地攻击者可在共享驱动器或非可移动介质中放置恶意的 autorun.inf 文件，指定替代程序执行路径，当其他用户访问该驱动器时系统会自动执行攻击者指定的恶意程序。该漏洞影响 Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具备本地访问权限或诱导用户访问特制驱动器方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0155"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:06.887","remediation":"在 Windows NT 4.0 中，通过注册表禁用非可移动介质的自动运行功能：将 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Policies\\Explorer` 下的 `NoDriveTypeAutoRun` 值设为 `0x000000FF`（禁用所有驱动器自动运行）。Windows 95/98 用户可在控制面板中关闭\"自动播放\"功能。建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本，这些版本默认对非可移动介质禁用 autorun.inf 自动执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/993","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-15&msg=000701bf79cd%24fdb5a620%244c4342a6%40mightye.org","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19754","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0155.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0155","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0155.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4d2ed764072119c12b6f84e6ee4e0df62586a8c4/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0155.json","https://github.com/nbrito/research/blob/f070ce78f917d962de8df74cc7a841f1cbbcfa00/cve/CVE-2000-0155/autorun.cpp","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-92rc-5g3w-9vp2/GHSA-92rc-5g3w-9vp2.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0155.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0139.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0139.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0139.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0506","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0506.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0161","title":"Microsoft Site Server Commerce Edition SQL注入漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server 3.0 Commerce Edition 自带的示例网站以及站点向导生成的代码，在接收用户输入的标识号后未进行充分验证，直接将其拼入 SQL 查询语句。攻击者只需向受影响页面提交含恶意 SQL 片段的请求，即可在无需身份验证的情况下操纵后端数据库，执行任意查询以读取敏感数据、篡改或删除记录，甚至可能获取数据库服务器的高级权限，造成数据泄露与业务中断。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0161"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-18","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Site Server 3.0 Commerce Edition 的 MS00-010 安全更新补丁（KB252614），该补丁修正了示例站点及向导生成代码中的用户输入验证缺陷。已使用受影响代码作为模板开发自定义站点的管理员，需参照 KB252614 中的代码示例，对所有用户输入实施严格验证，改用参数化查询或存储过程访问数据库，并确保 Web 应用使用的数据库账号仅授予最小必要权限。如暂无法立即打补丁，应临时下线所有基于受影响模板部署的示例站点，并在防火墙层限制对 Site Server 后端的直接数据库访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/994","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-010"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0506.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0143","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0143.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0159","title":"HP Ignite-UX 权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 系统的 Ignite-UX 在创建受信任系统的系统镜像时，未能正确保存 /etc/passwd 文件，导致镜像中账户密码字段被置为空值。本地或能访问该镜像的攻击者可借此以空白密码登录目标账户，从而非法提升自身权限至 root 或其他高权限用户。该漏洞影响使用 Ignite-UX 制作受信任系统镜像的 HP-UX 环境，攻击前提是攻击者能够访问包含空密码账户的镜像或已部署系统，利用方式是通过空密码认证获取本不应拥有的特权访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0159"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:07.393","remediation":"建议应用 HP 发布的 Ignite-UX 补丁（PHCO 系列补丁，如 PHCO_20765 及后续版本），修复镜像创建时不保存 /etc/passwd 导致密码字段为空的问题。升级后需检查所有由受信任系统镜像部署的主机，确认 /etc/passwd 及 /tcb 影子密码文件中 root 及各账户的密码字段非空，对空密码账户立即重设强密码并启用受信任系统（trusted system）模式，同时限制对镜像文件的访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-15&msg=20000217160216.13708.qmail%40underground.org","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a5db9ce197a4914a8237308d958cd159d8832fe6/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0159.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0159","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0159.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0159.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4hjr-mh66-rpm7/GHSA-4hjr-mh66-rpm7.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0159.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/27329332eaf6d7802a105e6a6dc78246a75b7339/2000.tsv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0143.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0142","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0142.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0158","title":"SCO OpenServer MMDF SMTP 缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO OpenServer 系统中的 MMDF 邮件服务器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向 SMTP 守护进程发送特制的超长 MAIL FROM 命令，触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取系统特权。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0158"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:07.263","remediation":"立即从 SCO 安全公告 SB-00.06a 获取并安装 MMDF 补丁，补丁位于 ftp://ftp.sco.com/SSE/security_bulletins/SB-00.06a。如无法打补丁，可在 SMTP 服务配置中限制 MAIL FROM 命令参数长度不超过 256 字节，或在网络边界防火墙封禁对 SMTP 端口（25）的非授权访问。由于 SCO OpenServer 已停止技术支持，建议迁移至受支持的 Linux 发行版或现代 UNIX 系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/997","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-15&msg=000001bf78af%246d0d47a0%244d2f45a1%40jmagdych.na.nai.com","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-15&msg=200002181449.JAA03436%40dragonfly.corp.home.net","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a5db9ce197a4914a8237308d958cd159d8832fe6/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0158.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0158","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0158.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0158.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-37h5-v582-hp97/GHSA-37h5-v582-hp97.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/