.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4d2ed764072119c12b6f84e6ee4e0df62586a8c4/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0156.json","https://github.com/biggerwing/nsfocus-rsas-knowledge-base/blob/156208b301d4649ead13cd15f827830d08245b89/example","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6rhq-4pc8-424f/GHSA-6rhq-4pc8-424f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0156.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001173.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5c0fb57d-4fb8-422c-91cf-624cc237111c.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0140.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0140.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0140.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0138","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0138.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0154","title":"SCO UnixWare ARCserve 代理本地符号链接漏洞","description":"tags.<value>SCO UnixWare 7.1/7.1.1 中的 ARCserve 代理存在符号链接攻击漏洞，本地攻击者可通过创建恶意符号链接指向任意文件，诱导 ARCserve 代理以特权写入或修改目标文件，从而实现任意文件修改。该漏洞影响 SCO UnixWare 7.1 和 7.1.1 版本，CVSS 评分 1.2，属于低危漏洞，攻击需要本地访问权限，利用方式为竞争条件下的符号链接替换。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0154"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:06.770","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止维护的 SCO UnixWare 7.1/7.1.1，官方已不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的操作系统平台（如现代 Linux 发行版）。如无法迁移，可采取以下缓解措施：1) 严格限制本地用户登录权限，仅允许受信任的管理员账户访问系统；2) 确保 /tmp 目录设置粘滞位（chmod 1777 /tmp），防止非属主删除或重命名临时文件；3) 使用文件系统 ACL 限制 ARCserve agent 对 /tmp 的写入范围；4) 监控 /tmp 目录的符号链接创建行为，通过审计日志及时发现异常。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.sco.com/security/","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/988","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-15&msg=000101bf78af%2494528870%244d2f45a1%40jmagdych.na.nai.com","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a5db9ce197a4914a8237308d958cd159d8832fe6/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0154.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0154","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0154.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0154.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6mjj-5236-h5mx/GHSA-6mjj-5236-h5mx.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0154.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001172.txt","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-2000.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0138.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0078","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0078.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0094","title":"FreeBSD/NetBSD/OpenBSD /proc 文件系统本地权限提升漏洞","description":"BSD 系统 /proc 文件系统存在权限检查缺失漏洞，本地攻击者可通过修改 stderr 文件描述符，利用 /proc/pid/mem 接口直接读写目标进程内存空间，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 3.4、NetBSD 1.4.1、OpenBSD 2.6 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0094"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:59.290","remediation":"升级到已修复此漏洞的 BSD 系统版本（FreeBSD 3.5+、NetBSD 1.5+、OpenBSD 2.7+）。如无法升级，可通过在 /etc/fstab 中移除 procfs 挂载或设置挂载选项为 nosuid 来禁用 /proc 文件系统，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/20760","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/940","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3995","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19726","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/94380d498cb52b65d051c9bd443b6f2aa85bf8ec/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0094.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0094","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0094.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cdbbe57bd34c799f670485304ef54912650bf03b/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0094.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-q6jp-4hpq-ccv5/GHSA-q6jp-4hpq-ccv5.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0094.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ef548566-276c-4499-8f90-1a0a9586f3c6.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0078.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0078.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0078.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0686","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0686.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0222","title":"Microsoft Windows 2000 ADMIN$共享未授权访问漏洞","description":"Windows 2000 在安装过程中直至系统首次重启前，管理员密码尚未激活生效，导致远程攻击者可在无需任何身份认证的情况下，通过网络共享协议直接连接目标系统的 ADMIN$ 隐藏共享目录，获取完全访问权限。该漏洞影响 Windows 2000 所有版本，攻击者只需知道目标 IP 地址即可在安装阶段未完成时实施攻击，可能导致系统被完全控制、敏感信息泄露或恶意软件植入。由于 ADMIN$ 共享拥有系统最高权限，攻击者可利用此漏洞在系统重启前执行任意操作。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0222"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:15.520","remediation":"安装 Windows 2000 后立即重启系统以激活 Administrator 密码；重启前勿将系统接入网络；安装后立即通过本地控制台设置强管理员密码；禁用不必要的 ADMIN$ 默认共享（net share ADMIN$ /delete）；升级至受支持的操作系统版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）以彻底规避此漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/990","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=20000215155750.M4500%40safe.hsc.fr","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58316128f65d22a226717ff1f92ebf2058e46bc6/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0222.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0222","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/2000/CVE-2000-0222/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0222.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8b7c7b13d1542fc7ddfb9cf48e51f3de3ab5c4ab/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0222.jso